# Added new internal endpoint to fetch configured feature flags

- Added a new internal endpoint `/i/get-configured-feature-flags` to `galley` that returns
  the server-wide feature flag defaults from the galley configuration
- Added a new operation `GetConfiguredFeatureFlags` to the `GalleyAPIAccess` effect
  to allow services to fetch feature flags from galley
- Updated `background-worker` to wire up the new endpoint:
  - Added `galley` endpoint configuration to `Opts`
  - Added `galleyEndpoint` field to `Env`
  - Updated `Registry` to call `getConfiguredFeatureFlags` and provide flags via `runInputSem`
